    {
      "bookmarkId": "41147996_58_5228-5306",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "5228-5306",
      "markText": "我称之为“毛伊习惯”(Maui Habit)。请你每天早晨一起床就立刻说出这句话：“今天又是美好的一天！”并在说出这句话的同时，尽量去感受乐观和积极的心态。",
      "totalCount": 8211,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41147996&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=5228&rangeEnd=5306",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/614325a07273de5c614b852?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=5228&rangeEnd=5306"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41147996_53_1332-1348",
      "chapterUid": 53,
      "range": "1332-1348",
      "markText": "愿望从来不会改变现实，行动才会。",
      "totalCount": 7200,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41147996&chapterUid=53&rangeStart=1332&rangeEnd=1348",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/614325a07273de5c614b852?chapterUid=53&rangeStart=1332&rangeEnd=1348"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41147996_62_1796-1879",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "1796-1879",
      "markText": "有没有什么可以提示你？是什么让这件事变得难以做到？在多数情况下，有些行为难以做到的根本原因不是缺乏动机。只要找到一个好的提示，或是让行为更容易做到，就能解决行为问题。",
      "totalCount": 6944,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41147996&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1879",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/614325a07273de5c614b852?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=1796&rangeEnd=1879"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41147996_59_1484-1579",
      "chapterUid": 59,
      "range": "1484-1579",
      "markText": "当动机(motivation)、能力(ability)和提示(prompt)同时出现的时候，行为就会发生。动机是做出行为的欲望，能力是去做某个行为的执行能力，而提示则是提醒你做出行为的信号。",
      "totalCount": 6840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41147996&chapterUid=59&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1579",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/614325a07273de5c614b852?chapterUid=59&rangeStart=1484&rangeEnd=1579"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "41147996_58_1594-1704",
      "chapterUid": 58,
      "range": "1594-1704",
      "markText": "停止自我批评； ·　把你的愿望拆解成微行为； ·　将每一次错误当成是一种新发现，并利用它们不断改进。",
      "totalCount": 6540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=41147996&chapterUid=58&rangeStart=1594&rangeEnd=1704",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/614325a07273de5c614b852?chapterUid=58&rangeStart=1594&rangeEnd=1704"
    },
    {
